*Smesta* je preselio u drugi grad. (He immediately moved to another city.)

*Smestio* je knjige u police. (He put the books into the shelves.)

*Smestiti* se na večeru bilo je čudno. (To settle for dinner was strange.)

*Smestiće* se u novu kuću uskoro. (He will soon move in to a new house.)

*Smestio* se u najbolju sobu. (He settled into the best room.)